<h2 id="travel-directions">Travel directions</h2>

<p>Visiting our Newport office? <a rel="external" href="https://www.google.com/maps/dir/Current+Location/Concept%20House,+Cardiff%20Rd,+Newport,+South%20Wales,+NP10%208QQ,+United%20Kingdom">View a map</a> and <a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20140711213904/http://www.ipo.gov.uk/about/contact/contact-directions/contact-directions-newport.htm">get directions</a></p>

<p>Visiting our London office? <a rel="external" href="https://www.google.com/maps/dir/Current+Location/4%20Abbey%20Orchard%20Street,+London,+SW1P%202HT,+United%20Kingdom">View a map</a> and <a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20140711213904/http://www.ipo.gov.uk/about/contact/contact-directions/contact-directions-london.htm">get directions</a></p>

<p>We have an electric vehicle charging point available for visitor use at our Newport site. This is a Fastcharge 7kW charger with two Type 2 sockets. Please contact the office in advance to check availability.</p>

<h2 id="disabled-access">Disabled access</h2>

<p>Information on <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/disabled-facilities-at-the-intellectual-property-office">disabled facilities for customers and visitors</a> to the Intellectual Property Office.</p>

